sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User
    participant UI as Web UI
    participant API as Backend API
    participant SF as Snowflake
    
    User->>UI: Access Application
    UI->>API: API Request
    API->>SF: Authenticate (OAuth)
    SF-->>API: Connected
    
    alt Read Data
        API->>SF: Query Source Data
        SF-->>API: Data
    else Transform Data
        API->>SF: Process & Transform
        SF-->>API: Complete
    end
    
    API-->>UI: Response
    UI-->>User: Display Results

